---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Home Stretch"
  description="Privacy Policy for Home Stretch: Moving Checklist iOS app."
>
  <div class="container section">
    <span class="section-label">// home stretch</span>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 5, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose privacy-prose">
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>Summary:</strong> Home Stretch does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Everything stays on your device.
      </div>

      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Home Stretch: Moving Checklist ("we", "our", or "the app") is a mobile application developed by Matt Donders.
        This Privacy Policy explains how the app handles your information.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>None.</strong> Home Stretch does not collect any personal information. The app:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Does not require an account or login</li>
        <li>Does not connect to the internet</li>
        <li>Does not use analytics or tracking</li>
        <li>Does not display advertisements</li>
        <li>Does not access your contacts, location, camera, microphone, or any other device sensors</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        All data you create in the app (your move date, checklist tasks, and custom tasks) is stored
        locally on your device using Apple's SwiftData framework. This data is never transmitted to any
        server or third party.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you delete the app, all associated data is permanently removed from your device.
      </p>

      <h2>In-App Purchases</h2>
      <p>
        Home Stretch offers a one-time in-app purchase to unlock premium features. All payment
        processing is handled entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not collect, store,
        or have access to any payment information such as credit card numbers or billing details.
      </p>
      <p>
        For information on how Apple handles your payment data, please refer to
        <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple's Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Home Stretch does not collect any data from anyone, including children. The app is safe for
        users of all ages.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Home Stretch does not integrate with any third-party services, SDKs, or APIs. The app
        functions entirely offline with no external dependencies.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this
        page with an updated "Last Updated" date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:matt@mattdonders.com">matt@mattdonders.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-subtle);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .privacy-prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .privacy-prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .privacy-prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .privacy-prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .highlight-box {
    background: var(--accent-dim);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .highlight-box strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
